reviewText:
the book came in good condition with my collection
thank you

Now, if this is for families and children, I would have to say,'NO!'. i know my views are held by a small minority, but they are still me views. This film did not do anything for my, nor for my children. My daughter, upon the completion of her first viewing of this video, exclaimed "Don't leave me hanging on an intellectual and visual level!" Perhaps other volumes of thiese videos are better, edited better, crafted better, but this one left a little to be desired. I wou7ld have expected much more, on an intellectual and philisophical level formt hese filmmakers.
